ingredients.text: Cheese and Onion Flavour Potato Crisps Ingredients
Rapeseed Vegetable Oils in varying proportions

product.ingredients_text:
Cheese & Onion Flavour Potato Crisps
Ingredients: Potatoes, Vegetable Oils (Sunflower, Rapeseed
in varying proportions), Cheese & Onion Seasoning [Dried
Onion, Sait, Dried Milk Whey, Lactose(from Milk, Sugar,
Flavouring (contains Mik, Cheese Powder (from Milk,
Dried Yeast, Acids (Citic Acid, Malic Acid), Whey Protein
(from Mik), Dried Garlic Colours (Annatto Bixin, Paprika
Extract), Antioxidants (Rosemary Extract, Ascorbic Acid
Tocopherol Rich Extract, Citric Acid).
